    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ha_integration_body",
      "x": 590,
      "y": 774,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 256,
      "text": "Device Control:\n  ha_call_service(domain, service, target, data)\n  ha_activate_scene(entity_id, transition)\n\nDevice Discovery & Reading:\n  ha_list_entities(domain, area)\n  ha_list_areas()  \u2022  ha_list_services(domain)\n  ha_get_entity_state(entity_id)\n  ha_render_template(template)\n\nHistorical Data:\n  ha_get_history(entity_ids, start, end)\n  ha_get_statistics(statistic_ids, start, end, period)\n\nDomain Coverage:\n  light, climate, switch, lock, sensor, binary_sensor\n  automation, scene, input_boolean, energy\n\nComfort Management:\n  Reads temp/humidity/air quality per room\n  Compares vs. memory comfort_preference facts\n  Adjusts climate, lighting, ventilation via services",
      "originalText": "Device Control:\n  ha_call_service(domain, service, target, data)\n  ha_activate_scene(entity_id, transition)\n\nDevice Discovery & Reading:\n  ha_list_entities(domain, area)\n  ha_list_areas()  \u2022  ha_list_services(domain)\n  ha_get_entity_state(entity_id)\n  ha_render_template(template)\n\nHistorical Data:\n  ha_get_history(entity_ids, start, end)\n  ha_get_statistics(statistic_ids, start, end, period)\n\nDomain Coverage:\n  light, climate, switch, lock, sensor, binary_sensor\n  automation, scene, input_boolean, energy\n\nComfort Management:\n  Reads temp/humidity/air quality per room\n  Compares vs. memory comfort_preference facts\n  Adjusts climate, lighting, ventilation via services",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
