    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "schema_body",
      "x": 1140,
      "y": 774,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 256,
      "text": "Core Tables:\n  devices            \u2014 registered HA entities + metadata\n  automations        \u2014 HA automations tracked by butler\n  scenes             \u2014 composed scenes + activation history\n  routines           \u2014 user-defined multi-step routines\n\nMonitoring Tables:\n  energy_readings    \u2014 consumption stats per device/period\n  environment_data   \u2014 temp, humidity, air quality snapshots\n\nApprovals Tables (from approvals module):\n  approval_rules     \u2014 standing rules (sensitivity + auto-approve)\n  pending_actions    \u2014 queued actions awaiting owner response\n\nShared Tables (shared.*):\n  contacts           \u2014 household members + owner identity\n  contact_info       \u2014 Telegram IDs, email addresses\n\nMemory Facts (memory module):\n  comfort_preference  \u2022  energy_baseline  \u2022  device_issue\n  scene_preference    \u2022  usage_pattern    \u2022  energy_pattern",
      "originalText": "Core Tables:\n  devices            \u2014 registered HA entities + metadata\n  automations        \u2014 HA automations tracked by butler\n  scenes             \u2014 composed scenes + activation history\n  routines           \u2014 user-defined multi-step routines\n\nMonitoring Tables:\n  energy_readings    \u2014 consumption stats per device/period\n  environment_data   \u2014 temp, humidity, air quality snapshots\n\nApprovals Tables (from approvals module):\n  approval_rules     \u2014 standing rules (sensitivity + auto-approve)\n  pending_actions    \u2014 queued actions awaiting owner response\n\nShared Tables (shared.*):\n  contacts           \u2014 household members + owner identity\n  contact_info       \u2014 Telegram IDs, email addresses\n\nMemory Facts (memory module):\n  comfort_preference  \u2022  energy_baseline  \u2022  device_issue\n  scene_preference    \u2022  usage_pattern    \u2022  energy_pattern",
